	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello All,<br>I know it's asking for alot, but,<br>I'm wondering if a couple of people wouldn't mind telling me of what armor/weapons they <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;      were/are using in the lvl 30-40 range.(I just hit lvl 30).<br>I'm just currious, I know I'm not the best player, and would just like to see where I stand<br>      amonst the other lvl 30-40 shamans out there.<br>Thank-you inadvance<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
